(Chit8 Ko3 Goeh8 Chit8 Pai2)
Sian-siN ka7 po3-choa2 khng3--leh, tui3 thai3-thai3 kong2: “Ti7 Pa-se, cha-pou lang5 na7 kap cha-bou2 lang5 siong-ho2 (cho3-ai3) liau2, cha-bou2--e5 ai3 hou7 cha-pou--e5 20 khou Bi2-kim. Chan2 ! Goa2 beh kin2 khi3 hia hiang2-siu7.”
“Goa2 ma7 beh khi3.” Thai3-thai3 ma7 kong2-oe7.
“Li2 beh khi3 hia chhong3 saN2?”
“Goa2 beh khoaN3 li2 chit8 ko3 goeh8 20 khou beh an2-choaN2 koe3-jit8?”
